{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji21.pdf"],"article":{"title":"致鼓荣臻电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致聂荣臻电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年7月5日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同意你们攻大同计划。望令张、罗、杨精心计划，充分准备，坚决夺取之。同时准备歼灭傅作义向我进攻之部队。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的致聂荣臻电的主要内容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]聂荣臻、刘澜涛6月24日致电中央军委，建议：“如政治上许可，在步骤上以攻占大同为有利，然后沿同蒲路南扫。”"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1946,"month":7,"day":5}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":462,"page_end":462},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"聂荣臻","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}